com.stabilit.sc.scmp
Class SCMPMessageID

java.lang.Object
  com.stabilit.sc.scmp.SCMPMessageID

public class SCMPMessageID
extends java.lang.Object

The Class SCMPMessageID. Responsible to provide correct message id for a specific request/response. Message id is unique for every message. Format: messageSequenceNr / partSequenceNr.

JTraber
